---
title: Caramelized Onion Hummus Serves 2 | with Roasted Chickpeas and Garlic Pita Chips
description: Creamy, wholesome hummus is made even more delicious with caramelized onions, smoky roasted chickpeas and fresh, bright parsley. You won't be able to resist diving in with warm garlic pita chips and scooping up every last bit!
